data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook22

data.value: Tautea o Hunting ia i runga i Pilgrimmage

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter1
data.value: 'Hāngai Ihirama te i runga i ngā mātāpono e rima.': Te tauākī o te peropheta (kani)

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter10
data.value: Ki te aroha ki te Ansar ko te tohu o te whakapono.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter12
data.value: Ki te rere (rere atu) i Al-Fitan (tamataraa me afflications etc) ko te wahi o te karakia.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter13
data.value: Te tauākī o te peropheta (kani): 'E mohio ana ahau Allah (azza wa jal) pai atu katoa o koutou mahi'.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter14
data.value: Te tangata e kino ana ki te hoki ki kufr.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter15
data.value: Ka te kōeke i te pai o te whakapono e rite ki a ratou mahi pai.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter16
data.value: Al-Haya ko te wahi o te whakapono.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter17
data.value: Te tauākī o Allah (azza wa jal): "Engari ki te ratou fakatomala, ka mahi Iqamat-rite-Salat [tuku Salat (pure) maitai], ka hoatu zakat ka waiho ratou ara free."

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter18
data.value: Ko te tangata e ta e whakapono ko mahi (mahi pai).

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter19
data.value: Ki te kore e awhi tetahi Ihirama pono, engari e pera i te faaheporaa no te wehi o te patua etc ranei

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter2
data.value: tikanga koutou Warua to koutou whakapono.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter20
data.value: Hei oha Ko te wahi o Ihirama.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter21
